description: Returns a list of all of the worker configurations in this account and Region.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the response of a ListWorkerConfigurations operation is truncated, it will include a NextToken. Send this NextToken in a subsequent request to continue listing from where the previous operation left off.

nested_items.name: workerConfigurations
nested_items.description: An array of worker configuration descriptions.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time that a worker configuration was created.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of a worker configuration.

nested_items.name: latestRevision
nested_items.description: The latest revision of a worker configuration.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time that a worker configuration revision was created.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of a worker configuration revision.

nested_items.name: revision
nested_items.description: The revision of a worker configuration.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the worker configuration.

nested_items.name: workerConfigurationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the worker configuration.

nested_items.name: workerConfigurationState
nested_items.description: The state of the worker configuration.
